data.description: Welcome to this stunning 3bed 2bath Rambler on 1/4 acre in the Tempo Lake community! Stylish entry flooring sets the tone for what lies ahead. The living room is a true centerpiece w/ its vaulted ceilings making it a cozy retreat w/ a free standing stove to warm up on a chilly PNW day. The kitchen is a chefs dream w/ new range hood & pristine pantry. New vinyl plank flooring & new SS fridge ties everything together. This lot is a true oasis w/ a secluded back patio for outdoor enjoyment. The upgrades are endless w/ newer flooring, interior paint, outlets, kitchen remodel, ceiling fans, energy-efficient LEDrecessed lighting & 240V plug for electric car charging. Conveniently near lake access, walking trails,parks,restaurants, schools & JBLM
